FBIS3-9702 "dreeu060_p_94004" FBIS-EEU-94-060 Document Type:Daily Report 29 Mar 1994 POLAND Further Reportage on Dariusz Rosati Candidacy Conservative Party on Rejection LD2903121794 Warsaw Radio Warszawa Network in Polish 1005 GMT 29 Mar 94 LD2903121794 Warsaw Radio Warszawa Network Language: Polish Article Type:BFN [Text] Aleksander Hall, chairman of the Conservative Party [PK], has expressed the view that the rejection of Dariusz Rosati's candidacy for the posts of deputy prime minister and minister of finance marks the beginning of Lech Walesa's presidential campaign. In an interview for Radio Zet, Hall described the recent events as another step undermining democracy.
